---
import BlogPost from '@/layouts/BlogPost.astro';

const title = "Family Reunion Rentals: Large Property Strategy for CNY";
const description = "Optimize your 3-4 bedroom Melaka property for Chinese New Year family reunions. Targeting multi-generational groups, pricing for large groups, and amenity requirements.";
const date = "2026-01-30";
const category = "comparison";
const language = "en";
const image = "/images/blog/family-reunion-cny-strategy.jpg";

const content = `
<h1>Family Reunion Rentals: Large Property Strategy for CNY</h1>

<p>Chinese New Year 2026 represents the <strong>biggest opportunity</strong> for owners of 3+ bedroom properties in Melaka. Multi-generational families seeking reunion accommodations drive <strong>premium demand for spacious rentals</strong> with specific requirements.</p>

<h2>The Multi-Generational CNY Guest</h2>

<p><strong>Typical reunion group composition:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li><strong>Size:</strong> 6-10 people (3 generations)</li>
<li><strong>Duration:</strong> 3-5 nights (CNY Eve - Day 3 most popular)</li>
<li><strong>Budget:</strong> RM 1,000-1,500/night (3-4BR units)</li>
<li><strong>Requirements:</strong> Multiple bathrooms, kitchen, common areas, heritage experience</li>
</ul>

<h3>Property Requirements for Reunions</h3>

<p><strong>Essential amenities:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li><strong>Sleeping:</strong> Private bedrooms for each couple/family unit</li>
<li><strong>Bathrooms:</strong> Minimum 2 bathrooms (3 preferred for 8+ guests)</li>
<li><strong>Common space:</strong> Living room for family gatherings</li>
<li><strong>Kitchen:</strong> Full kitchen for reunion dinner preparation</li>
<li><strong>Parking:</strong> 2+ cars (multiple families driving separately)</li>
<li><strong>WiFi:</strong> Strong connection for kids/guests working remotely</li>
</ul>

<h2>CNY Pricing for Large Groups</h2>

<p><strong>Premium strategy for 3-4BR units:</strong></p>

<table class="w-full">
<thead>
<tr>
<th><strong>Unit Type</strong></th>
<th><strong>Standard Rate</strong></th>
<th><strong>CNY Rate</strong></th>
<th><strong>Minimum Stay</strong></th>
</tr>
</thead>
<tbody>
<tr>
<td>3BR condo</td>
<td>RM 300-350</td>
<td>RM 550-650</td>
<td>4 nights</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>4BR house</td>
<td>RM 400-450</td>
<td>RM 700-850</td>
<td>5 nights</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>Heritage shophouse (3BR)</td>
<td>RM 450-500</td>
<td>RM 900-1,000</td>
<td>5 nights</td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>

<p><strong>Per-person pricing:</strong> Families divide costs 6-10 ways, making large properties <strong>more affordable per person</strong> than booking multiple smaller units.</p>

<h2>Reunion-Specific Marketing</h2>

<p><strong>Listing emphasis:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>"Perfect for 3-generation family reunions - 3 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms"</li>
<li>"Host CNY reunion dinner in our heritage shophouse dining room"</li>
<li>"Multiple common areas for family bonding time"</li>
<li>"Kids can run around, grandparents can relax"</li>
</ul>

<p><strong>Targeting:</strong> Facebook family groups, SG reunion organizers, family WhatsApp chains.</p>

<p><strong>WhatsApp +60166996688</strong> for large property CNY optimization.</p>
`;
---

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>{title}</title>
    <meta name="description" content={description}>
</head>
